criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI > 25 Kg/m2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Malignant neoplasia;

          -  Current use of psychotropic drugs;

          -  Chronic renal failure;

          -  Pituitary macroadenomas and craniopharyngiomas;

          -  Contraindications to MRI execution (p. e. pace-maker, metal foreign bodies like
             slivers, non MRI compatible vascular clips or prosthesis)
